*   ## **_MENS MONEY IN THE BANK: DREW MCINTYRE DEF. JEY USO, LA KNIGHT, CARMELO HAYES, CHAD GABLE AND ANDRADE_**
    

Excellent Ladder Match with a ton of great bumps. The heavy advertising for the Boys as if WWE actually existed in their universe was cool.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e57164a9-4e5d-48f3-a506-5ab618a6dc8e/20240706_170229.jpg)

*   ## **_WWE INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: SAMI ZAYN DEF. BRON BREAKKER_**
    

Very surprising result after a well performed, straight forward David vs Goliath match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9c0b3d83-ff76-4793-af3d-f2df692bd1c2/PhotoGrid_1_20240706171951.jpg)

John Cena will officially have his final run in WWE starting January 1st with the first WWE Raw on Netflix and ending with WrestleMania in Las Vegas.

#ThankYouCena

